lead_paragraph: A Spanish corruption case surrounding Neymar's transfer from Santos to Barcelona in 2013 is certain to influence the Brazil forward's form, national team coach Tite said on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Corruption Case a Complication for Neymar, Says Brazil Coach
